databases.test_throttle.throttle.display_name.throttle_overview=\
A "throttle" rule will batch up several notifications to the same group into a single action.\
<br>\
<br>\
Actions can be associated with various "storm" levels.\  The handling of a relatively infrequent \
stream of events (say 1 event every minute) should be different from a very large stream of events \
(20 events per second).  \
<br>\
<br>\
There are three levels of storms that can be specified at the current time. and there three different \
types of actions that can be associated with each storm level.


